title: FIFA 14 1.3.0 (Latest version!)
description:
FIFA 14 V 1.3.0 for android.

NO virus
NO spyware.

It contains a single (cracked) apk.

Instructions to unlock the premium options.

Download the apk and install it using your file manager.
Execute it and wait for the download to end.
Skip the tutorial and go to the main menu.
Go to the tab "play" and touch the little lock icon.
Touch the "restore previous purchases" button and DONE.

Now you have FIFA 14 totally unlocked!

It really works.

Tested with a nexus 7 (2012) and without a previous purchase.

Enjoy and seed.
